### Command:

```bash

ls -l 
ls -la
ls -li
ls -ltr
ls -h -l #human redable format
top -b -n 1
```
## greep command

```bash
grep  # Regular grep
egrep # Extended grep for regular expression
fgrep # Fixed string separated by new line
rgrep # Reverse grep


```
egrep & fgrep depricated 

```
bash grep -E and grep -F can be used 
```